<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="Medi-Hub2.png">
    <title>Verify Prescription - MediHub</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0ede6;
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: #1a2e2a;
        }

        /* ── Navbar ── */
        nav {
            background: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0 48px;
            height: 64px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e4dc;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a2e2a;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #4a5e58;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        .nav-links a.active {
            background: #d4f0e8;
            color: #1a7a5e;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover:not(.active) {
            background: #f0ede6;
        }

        .btn-upload-nav {
            background: #1a7a5e;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            padding: 10px 20px !important;
            border-radius: 8px !important;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .btn-upload-nav:hover {
            background: #155f4a !important;
        }

        /* ── Page layout ── */
        .page-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
            padding: 60px 24px;
            min-height: calc(100vh - 64px);
        }

        /* ── Card ── */
        .confirm-container {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 48px 52px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 560px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(26, 42, 38, 0.08);
        }

        /* ── Breadcrumb ── */
        .breadcrumb {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            background: #d4f0e8;
            color: #1a7a5e;
            font-size: 0.72rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 5px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .breadcrumb::before {
            content: '✦';
            font-size: 0.65rem;
        }

        /* ── Heading ── */
        .confirm-container h1 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #1a2e2a;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .confirm-container h1 span {
            color: #1a7a5e;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #6b7e78;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
        }

        /* ── Divider ── */
        .divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid #e8e4dc;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        /* ── Fields ── */
        .field {
            margin-bottom: 22px;
        }

        .field label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #4a5e58;
            letter-spacing: 0.03em;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .field input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border: 1.5px solid #dde8e4;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #1a2e2a;
            background: #f8faf9;
            outline: none;
            transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, background 0.2s;
        }

        .field input:focus {
            border-color: #1a7a5e;
            background: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(26, 122, 94, 0.12);
        }

        .field input::placeholder {
            color: #a0b0aa;
        }

        /* ── Medicines table ── */
        .medicines-label {
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #4a5e58;
            letter-spacing: 0.03em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .medicine-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .medicine-row input {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 11px 14px;
            border: 1.5px solid #dde8e4;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            color: #1a2e2a;
            background: #f8faf9;
            outline: none;
            transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }

        .medicine-row input:focus {
            border-color: #1a7a5e;
            background: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(26, 122, 94, 0.12);
        }

        /* ── Actions ── */
        .actions {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            margin-top: 36px;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            flex: 1;
            background: #1a7a5e;
            color: #ffffff;
            border: none;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.1s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #155f4a;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(26, 122, 94, 0.28);
        }

        .btn-primary:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
        }

        .btn-cancel {
            color: #4a5e58;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1.5px solid #dde8e4;
            background: transparent;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .btn-cancel:hover {
            background: #f0ede6;
            border-color: #c8c0b4;
        }

        /* ── Info badge ── */
        .info-badge {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 10px;
            background: #eaf7f2;
            border: 1px solid #b6e8d4;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #1a7a5e;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .info-badge svg {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav>
        <a href="/home" class="logo">
            <svg class="logo-icon" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <rect width="36" height="36" rx="10" fill="#d4f0e8"/>
                <path d="M18 8v20M8 18h20" stroke="#1a7a5e" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <circle cx="18" cy="18" r="4" fill="#1a7a5e" opacity="0.3"/>
            </svg>
            MediHub
        </a>

        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/home" class="active">Home</a>
            <a href="/prescriptions">Your Prescriptions</a>
            <a href="/reminder">Reminder</a>
        </div>

        <a href="/upload" class="nav-links btn-upload-nav">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/>
                <polyline points="17 8 12 3 7 8"/>
                <line x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="15"/>
            </svg>
            Upload Prescription
        </a>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main -->
    <div class="page-wrapper">
        <section class="confirm-container">

            <div class="breadcrumb">Smart Health Management</div>

            <h1>Verify <span>Extracted</span> Information</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Review the details pulled from your prescription and correct anything if needed.</p>

            <hr class="divider">

            <div class="info-badge">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/>
                </svg>
                Please verify the auto-filled fields below. Accurate information ensures better reminders and health tracking.
            </div>

            <form action="/save-to-db" method="POST">
                <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= result.id %>">

                <div class="field">
                    <label>Doctor Name</label>
                    <input type="text" name="doctor_name" value="<%= result.doctor_name || '' %>" placeholder="e.g. Dr. Anjali Sharma">
                </div>

                <div class="field">
                    <label>Next Visit Date</label>
                    <input type="date" name="next_visit" value="<%= result.next_visit || '' %>" placeholder="e.g. 10 April 2025">
                </div>

                <div class="actions">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
                        </svg>
                        Finalize &amp; Save
                    </button>
                    <a href="/home" class="btn-cancel">Cancel</a>
                </div>
            </form>

        </section>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
```